reviews.text:
Ordered
three types of rolls. When they arrived, they all turned out to be spoiled fish and had to be thrown away. Horror

I'm not in the habit of writing negative reviews, but these were the worst rolls I've ever eaten - with undercooked rice that crunched on my teeth!!! Money down the drain!!!

I ordered through Glovo at Shcherbakovsky, 16. The order was made today.

The website states that the order is over UAH 350. - delivery is free.
We had an order for 390 hryvnias, while they charged 20 hryvnias for delivery.
Sushi is delicious, but!
The fish is cut unevenly, torn.
The order was for two people. There was only one sauce.
The sauce was immediately poured into a plastic container, which spilled during transportation. In the end, there was very little sauce left.
Is it better to pack the sauce in a vacuum bag?
Roe of flying fish. Floated!
There was very little of it. It seems that when sushi was made, it was licked with the tongue.))

Sushi is not tasty. We ordered delivery 4 hours before the required time (actually quite in advance) and firstly, it was delivered 40 minutes later, and secondly, the sushi was not tasty, the rice was overcooked (that’s why everything stuck together), but at the same time this sushi is still fell apart anyway. I really don't recommend it

You didn't even have to order to be disappointed.

1. The operator called back with a delay of 15 minutes, and communicated as if doing a huge favor. I'm not asking for any respect, just a little courtesy.
2. There will be no free shipping if you take promotional items. They wanted to charge more for delivery than Glovo.
3. A set of 5 rolls includes ONE portion of sauce and wasabi. I asked to add 4 more, they told me that it was an additional 120 hryvnias.
Once again, 30 hryvnias for one small set of sauce + wasabi.
4. The cost of the order increased by 50%. I said I wanted to cancel it and the operator silently hung up.

Would have given 1 star, but maybe you have delicious rolls. Too bad I won't try.

============================================
Renewal
============================================

They responded quite promptly, offered recruitment on somewhat preferential terms and apologized for the first conversation.

Rolls are really tasty! :)

Thank you.
